✔ Summarize project shortly @done(25-12-13 09:45)
    - App to allow input of travel expenses for a specific date and will store the information to keep track on expenses for specific types over a certain time frame
☐ Define key functions and features @started(25-12-13 09:45)
    - Input of expenses in three different currencies (USD, JPY, EUR)
    - Add date when the expense was done
    - Add category (Train, Hotel, etc.)
    - Add label company card or self expense
    - Add for each item if a daily allowance applies (3000 JPY for half day and 6000 for overnight)
    - Have an overview of all expenses in a specific month 
    - mark Items as "billed" and put them in archive
    - Showing a sub-total of expenses for each months
    - App should work on web / desktop and phone 
    - Create PDF of weekly/monthly items for print
☐ Define necessary tools and stack
    ☐ Frontend: 
        - Vanilla HTML/CSS/JS
        - Responsive UI (CSS Grid/Flex, Mobile-first)
        - PWA (?)
        - manifest.json (?)
        - Service Worker (Workbox?)
        - IndexedDB (besser als localStorage)
        - localForage
    ☐ Build/Dev Tools
        - Vite 
        - ESLite + Prettier
        - Datum/Zeitzone: Luxon
☐ Future features
    - Possibility to print one months expense items in a specific form to print and hand over to accounting

