☐ Project-Skeleton (Html + CSS + Scripts)
    ☐ index.html
    ☐ styles.css
    ☐ app.js (wiring + events)
    ☐ storage.js (load/save)
    ☐ domain.js (totals, validation, format)
    ☐ ui.js (render table, render totals)

☐ Storage.js: loadState() / saveState(state)
☐ State-Shape: { months: { [monthId]: MonthRecord }, activeMonthId }
☐ UI-Render: Month-list + Table render
☐ Add-Expense: Button -> state push -> save -> render
☐ Delete Expense: Button -> remove -> save -> render
☐ Edit Expense: "Edit" Save replace item
☐ Totals: Total + per category calculate and show
☐ Sort by date
☐ PDF/Print @media print + "Print" button (window.print())